220
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,280
Ruthie Sayles.

221
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:30,310
Dizem que torceu o tornozelo
ao cair da passadeira.

222
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,550
